title: Butternut squash soup with spinach ravioli
ingredients: ['1/4 teaspoon ground cumin', '1/4 teaspoon ground nutmeg', '50g butter', '170g sliced onions', '70g sliced leeks', '350g peeled, seeded and cubed butternut squash', '125ml dry white wine', '1L chicken stock', '1 pinch ground cinnamon', '1 pinch ground ginger', '1 (500g) packet cheese and spinach ravioli', '180ml single cream', 'salt and pepper to taste']
